Installation/ Running

    clone the repository https://github.com/evan-mitchell93/iuni.git

    run pip install -r requirements.txt to install required packages

    run python3 main.py to start the application


Usage
    in the browser go to https//127.0.0.1:5000 to view the application  

    use the dropdown box to select one of the timezones

    click the submit button to get the current time in the selected timezone


